    <h1 class="headline large"><%= link_to "General Potter Farm", "http://generalpotterfarm.com/", :target => "_blank" %></h1>

    <%= image_tag 'general_potter_farm.jpg' %>

    <p>The <%= link_to "General Potter Farm", "http://generalpotterfarm.com/", :target => "_blank" %> is a renovated, 2-story <%= link_to "bank barn", "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_barn", :target => "_blank" %>, built in the 1830s.</p>
